Sentencas: By inserting 2 three-dimensional (3D) printed interconnectors, a pencil stack is fabricated by electrically connecting 3 single solid oxide fuel cells in series.
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The open-circuit voltage exhibits higher than 3 V using this bamboo-like connecting mode.
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interconnector consists of Ti-containing 316 stainless steel, and the weight of it varies only 0.5% at temperatures over the range of 25-800 degrees C under oxidation conditions.
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The outer diameter of the cell is 10 mm, while the thickness of the electrolyte is about 5 mm.
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: When operated on hydrogen, the maximum power density of the 3-cells in series double its value compare with that of the cell with the same axial length.
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The 3-cells stack in series shows a maximum power of 11.5 W at 700 degrees C, which corresponds to a high power density of 0.36 W cm2.(c) 2023
Titulo: A 3D printed redox-stable interconnector for bamboo-like tubular solid oxide fuel cells
